                                <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="2019-05-26">
                                <p itemprop="description">Royal Realty has been taking care of our property as our property manager for a little under a year and it has been fantastic so far. We really appreciate the responsiveness, the smooth process, and just how easy it was for us. Jennifer has been amazing to work with. Thank you :)<p>
                            </div>

                            <div itemprop="review" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
                                <meta itemprop="author" content="Liz P.">
                                <div itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Rating">
                                    <meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="4.0">
                                </div>
                                <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="2019-06-01">
                                <p itemprop="description">Working with Lynell H at Royal Realty has been very pleasant experience. She quickly response back via text, phone, and email which is very important and appreciated as a renter. I highly recommend her and Royal Realty to my friends and family.
                                    &#34;Thank you Lynell for all the accommodations&#34;<p>
                            </div>

                            <div itemprop="review" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
                                <meta itemprop="author" content="Carissa H.">
                                <div itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Rating">
                                    <meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5.0">
                                </div>
                                <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="2019-02-11">
                                <p itemprop="description">I couldn&#39;t be happier with the experience I&#39;ve had with Royal Realty. I was a tenant at one of Jacqueline Little&#39;s management properties. I would definitely recommend her if your looking for a professional property manager. Rest assured your property is in good hands. She was the point person from the initial viewing to the final walk through. I have worked with Jacqueline for over a year and she and her team have been great. I have been very satisfied with her service and would definitely want to work with her when in need of real estate or property management assistance. Any time I needed to contact her she was always on top of getting a back to me and helped resolve any issues that arose. She is very caring and provides a personal touch that makes you feel like a valued customer.<p>
                            </div>

                            <div itemprop="review" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
                                <meta itemprop="author" content="Chris J.">
