                                <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="2018-12-06">
                                <p itemprop="description">Amazing all around!

                                    We recently purchased our vacation condo and needed a reputable property management company to represent us.

                                    We found it with Royal Realty. Our agent representative Casey went above and beyond to assist us in getting our condo ready for short term rental. We live in California so communication was crucial in all the steps and Casey was attentive and very, very organized! (We thought we were organized but he takes it to another level) He was there to represent us, when our new furniture arrived he was there to coordinate the setup and also stood in for us when the keys to the condo were delivered. Again above and beyond!

                                    Overall because of working with Casey and his company, we never felt pressured or ignored he made the process so smooth. We never had any doubts about the handling of our property.

                                    We will continue to use his services and also recommend anyone to Royal Realty without any hesitation!

                                    Thank you again Casey for your continued hard work!

                                    Mahalo!

                                    - The Jio&#39;s<p>
                            </div>

                            <div itemprop="review" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
                                <meta itemprop="author" content="TrevorL D.">
                                <div itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Rating">
                                    <meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5.0">
                                </div>
                                <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="2018-04-12">
                                <p itemprop="description">Shari Sodetani &amp; The Team at Royal Realty, LLC were a delightful combination of: professionalism &amp; genuine client care

                                    * genuine client care:
                                    + excellent detailed communication (via preferred method)
                                    + listens, makes notes, and then actions.
                                    + timely responsiveness
                                    + from start to finish ~ alongside you

                                    Professionalism:
                                    + team
                                    + industry knowledge
                                    + presentation
                                    + values: hard work, listening, communication, integrity, honesty, follow up / through, equipping others, etc.

                                    Highly recommend.

                                    10 Stars In My Book<p>
                            </div>

                            <div itemprop="review" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
                                <meta itemprop="author" content="Juliana B.">
                                <div itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Rating">
                                    <meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5.0">
                                </div>
                                <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="2018-03-15">
                                <p itemprop="description">Jacqueline Little is the most attentive &amp; professional property manager I have ever done business with. She has a very understanding demeanor and every time I had an issue, it was handled with a sense of urgency and importance - She NEVER made me feel like &#34;just another tenant&#34;, but more like a family member that needed her immediate attention. It is rare to find such a GEM in the world of Property Management these days :) Mahalo Jacky!

                                    I also had the pleasure of receiving assistance from Shari Sodetani - she too is both organized and professional. These ladies just make you feel like a priority and everything was handled so efficiently!

                                    SUCH GREAT SERVICE FROM THE TEAM AT ROYAL REALTY - THANKS AGAIN!!<p>
                            </div>

                            <div itemprop="review" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
                                <meta itemprop="author" content="Yu G.">
                                <div itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Rating">
                                    <meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5.0">
                                </div>
                                <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="2018-09-18">
                                <p itemprop="description">it is a breeze to work with them, they got my property rent out the same month I started with them. If you want a care-free property management, they are your choice.<p>
                            </div>

                            <div itemprop="review" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
                                <meta itemprop="author" content="Puanani O.">
                                <div itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Rating">
                                    <meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5.0">
                                </div>
                                <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="2018-09-19">
                                <p itemprop="description">Monica Kamaka Cooper has assisted our family for
                                    The last few years with renting out our former family home.  She is professional and thoughtful.  She was a godsend when my dad suddenly passed away in 2016.  She has been efficient in handling all requests from the tenants.  We really appreciate everything she does
                                    For
                                    Us.<p>
                            </div>

                            <div itemprop="review" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
                                <meta itemprop="author" content="Alan K.">
                                <div itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Rating">
                                    <meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5.0">
                                </div>
                                <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="2018-05-10">
                                <p itemprop="description">Jacqueline Little and staff do an amazing job! She took over my condo from a lame property manager an did excellent job from renovation to quickly finding a new tenant. Apparently basic things like courtesy, being available for communication, and getting stuff done in a timely manner is too hard for a lot of property managers...You will NOT have these issues with Jacqueline.
                                    After my previous tenant moved out, she gave some renovation suggestions which I opted to do and had contractors available to do the work asap. Everything is well documented from the contractor that was used, cost, and scheduling. A lot of online sites was used to market the unit and they also created a video walk through. I was regularly updated on showings which was important to me in case we needed to adjust the rental price.
                                    It&#39; been a couple of months and have had no issues. Payment is on time and I&#39;m given a detailed invoice. I should add that I&#39;m working overseas and have never met Jacqueline in person. Everything that was done was through phone and emails. Highly recommended and will work with again!<p>
                            </div>

                            <div itemprop="review" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
                                <meta itemprop="author" content="Roman P.">
                                <div itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Rating">
                                    <meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5.0">
                                </div>
                                <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="2018-02-26">
                                <p itemprop="description">I had a great experience working with Frances Sagun! She was very prompt with responding to text messages and phone calls. I also had a great experience working with Shari Sodetani she is very professional. I can tell that both these ladies enjoy their job and enjoy helping people! I would recommend choosing to work with these ladies! You will not be disappointed!<p>
                            </div>

                            <div itemprop="review" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
                                <meta itemprop="author" content="Matt S.">
                                <div itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Rating">
                                    <meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5.0">
                                </div>
                                <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="2018-03-05">
                                <p itemprop="description">Shari Sodetani was amazing to work with! She is a proven professional with backed by years of experience. With the support of Royal Realty and their team, she stands above the crowd in her industry. She is organized, very punctual and and takes great care of her clients!<p>
                            </div>

                            <div itemprop="review" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
                                <meta itemprop="author" content="Henry B.">
                                <div itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Rating">
                                    <meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5.0">
                                </div>
                                <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="2018-03-06">
                                <p itemprop="description">Shari Sodetani knows her stuff.  I spent 15 years in Real Estate and did not know what to make of her at first.   Rarely have I seen an agent do the kind of research that she does whether it is a listing or rental.   There is a reason she is the best.<p>
                            </div>

                            <div itemprop="review" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
                                <meta itemprop="author" content="CJ C.">
                                <div itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Rating">
                                    <meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5.0">
                                </div>
                                <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="2018-03-05">
                                <p itemprop="description">Shari Sodetani is an amazing agent. Buying, selling, renting or property management... she can do it all!  She will go above and beyond to service her clients needs. This review doesn&#39;t do justice to how great of a job she does. Please contact her if you need an agent!<p>
                            </div>

                            <div itemprop="review" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
                                <meta itemprop="author" content="K B.">
                                <div itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Rating">
                                    <meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5.0">
                                </div>
                                <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="2018-04-10">
                                <p itemprop="description">Jennifer Peele has been a tremendous blessing to me, going above and beyond to help me through the rental process . My roommate is on the mainland so everything had to be done via Internet,  and for two old ladies, that was challenging.  We couldn&#39;t have done it without Jennifer&#39;s patience and help.  Jennifer has also been a terrific property manager, making sure things are right (this is the first time this unit has been a rental) and everything is in excellent working order.  She was even more concerned than I was about the appliances, which are fine.  As soon as I signed the lease, Jennifer called an appliance repairman to make sure the gas range was working correctly  (it looked quite new to me), so I could cook Easter dinner on the 1st.
                                    A big Mahalo to Jennifer and Royal Realty!<p>
                            </div>

                            <div itemprop="review" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
                                <meta itemprop="author" content="Nicole T.">
                                <div itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Rating">
                                    <meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5.0">
                                </div>
                                <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="2018-02-12">
                                <p itemprop="description">Shari Sodetani is fantastic! She is extremely personable, professional, and quick to respond to any issues you may have, going above and beyond to make sure any problem is resolved. Highly recommended!<p>
                            </div>

                            <div itemprop="review" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
                                <meta itemprop="author" content="Marita H.">
                                <div itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Rating">
                                    <meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5.0">
                                </div>
                                <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="2018-12-26">
                                <p itemprop="description">I have recently been working with Kris Masaki in helping me relocate to Hawaii. I cannot express what a joy it has been working with him. He has taken almost all of the stress out of this process for me. From accommodating virtual tours, to helping me with unexpected pacakage deliveries, he has been so patient and kind when working with me! I would absolutely recommend Royal Realty to anyone! Thank you, Kris and Royal Realty!<p>
                            </div>

                            <div itemprop="review" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
                                <meta itemprop="author" content="Elijah H.">
                                <div itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Rating">
                                    <meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5.0">
                                </div>
                                <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="2018-03-30">
                                <p itemprop="description">I&#39;ve been a part of Shari Sodetani&#39;s team as her intern/assistant for almost a year now, and I&#39;ve been a tenant of hers for the past 4 months, and through both experiences, I can say that there are few agents who are as knowledgeable, experienced, motivated and genuine as she is.

                                    As her intern/assistant, I&#39;ve gained valuable knowledge as to the ins and outs of property management, and being able to learn her systems and processes has truly been a blessing. Shari differs from other agents in that she goes above and beyond to service and protect her owners, always being prepared, timely, and ready to take on any situation presented to her. She also cares about her tenants and handles every situation/obstacle to the best of her ability. There&#39;s a reason she has a strong network and referrals going her way all the time -- she&#39;s trustworthy and builds strong relationships with everyone she encounters.

                                    As her current tenant, I&#39;ve had an excellent experience. She is prompt when dealing with repairs/issues with my unit, and when first checking me into my unit, she was very helpful in making sure I understood every part of the lease. She didn&#39;t hesitate in answering my questions, and she has been constantly helpful.

                                    Shari is of the best of the best, and I highly recommend her to anyone looking for a property manager or realtor.<p>
                            </div>

                            <div itemprop="review" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
                                <meta itemprop="author" content="Chris K.">
                                <div itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Rating">
                                    <meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5.0">
                                </div>
                                <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="2018-05-16">
                                <p itemprop="description">I can&#39;t express enough just how awesome it was having Kris Masaki as a property manager while I was a renter. He was really easy to work with, patient, and understanding. When I had a couple issues with my apartment, he got back to me right away and had people in there quickly to remedy the situations that arose (ie. the very start of termites showing themselves, a leaky faucet, etc.). He was extremely cool when it came to moving out too. It was a pretty stressful time for me, but working with Kris definitely made the process easier. Eventually, I would love to be able to have Kris as a property manager for my rental(s) because I know he&#39;d take great care of me as well as the renter! =)<p>
                            </div>

                            <div itemprop="review" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
                                <meta itemprop="author" content="Davy S.">
                                <div itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Rating">
                                    <meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5.0">
                                </div>
                                <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="2018-05-12">
                                <p itemprop="description">So glad we ran into Royal Realty and Kris Masaki. We originally went to see a unit and realizing it wasn&#39;t fitting what we were looking for, Kris came up with many great options of availability that would match our needs. We ended renting a unit we really like and the service of communication, being there before visiting the location multiple times, providing the necessary fixes we needed for the unit in a timely matter has been a great and smooth experience. We are glad have a good property manager. Thank you.<p>
                            </div>

                            <div itemprop="review" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
                                <meta itemprop="author" content="Bryan V.">
                                <div itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Rating">
                                    <meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5.0">
                                </div>
                                <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="2017-12-07">
                                <p itemprop="description">I just thought all property management companies here were awful and it was just part of renting.  Jacqueline Little was my recent property manager was very pleasant to work with.  She was very approachable and quick to respond.  I&#39;d gladly go with Royal Realty for any property management, rental, or sales.<p>
                            </div>


                        </div>

                    </div>





